  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg/400px-Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"602\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/aa/Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg/600px-Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/aa/Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg/800px-Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Iron_Islands_AFFC_map.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Copyright ©Random House, drawn by James Sinclair</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Map of the Iron Islands</b> in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> consists of all the geographical information given of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a> and the western part of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> that is closest to the Iron Islands.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_Listed\">Places Listed</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Feast_for_Crows-Map_of_the_Iron_Islands&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places Listed\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ashemark\" title=\"Ashemark\">Ashemark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Banefort\" title=\"Banefort\">Banefort</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Blacktyde\" title=\"Blacktyde\">Blacktyde</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Rush\" title=\"B